name: <path::Components<'a> as core::cmp::PartialEq>::eq

core::cmp::PartialEq::eq.doc: Tests for `self` and `other` values to be equal, and is used by `==`.

core::iter::Iterator::eq.doc:
Determines if the elements of this [`Iterator`] are equal to those of
 another.

 # Examples

 ```
 assert_eq!([1].iter().eq([1].iter()), true);
 assert_eq!([1].iter().eq([1, 2].iter()), false);
 ```
